<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1183589>
    dc:description "Figs 33 - 34. Known distributions of the genera Smeringopus Simon, 1890 and Spermophora Hentz, 1841 in Central Africa. For detailed distribution maps of Smeringopus species see Huber (2012). Question marks denote uncertain identifications (females from Cameroon; one pair from Príncipe Island)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/1183589/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

